                                    <p>The process begins as soon as your parcel is securely received in our warehouse.
                                        Every item
                                        is
                                        accurately recorded to
                                        ensure total traceability.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <i class="step-line" />
                                <div class="number font-dosis">1</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="steps-container">
                                <div class="content">
                                    <h2>Expert Packaging</h2>
                                    <p>Our team of packaging experts spring into action. Every product is treated with care
                                        and
                                        packed to
                                        professional
                                        standards, guaranteeing maximum protection during transit.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <i class="step-line" />
                                <div class="number font-dosis">2</div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="steps-container">
                                <div class="content">
