                                        your
                                        parcel
                                        from our warehouse to
                                        its final delivery, giving you total peace of mind.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <i class="step-line" />
                                <div class="number font-dosis">4</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="steps-container">
                                <div class="content">
                                    <h2>Serene Delivery</h2>
                                    <p>Our commitment doesn't stop with the packaging. We ensure that every parcel arrives
                                        at its
                                        destination in perfect
                                        condition. Your satisfaction is our top priority with every delivery.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <i class="step-line" />
                                <div class="number font-dosis">5</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
