                    </h1>

                    <hr class="border-2 rounded-lg my-4 border-blue-green w-[5rem]" />
                </div>
                <div
                    class="w-full max-w-[90rem] px-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-around xl:justify-between gap-y-1">
                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 w-full max-w-md md:w-[48%] xl:w-1/4 min-h-[14rem] xl:-ml-4 p-4 hover:border rounded-md hover:shadow-lg shadow-slate-500 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
                        <div class="text-green-steel text-4xl leading-none">
