                        <h2 class="text-xl font-dosis -mb-2 font-medium text-green-steel">
                            Maximum parcel Security
                        </h2>
                        <p class="font-open-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
                            We put the safety of your parcels first. Every step, from receipt to delivery, is meticulously
                            managed to ensure maximum
                            security.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 w-full max-w-md md:w-[48%] xl:w-1/4 min-h-[14rem]  p-4 hover:border rounded-md hover:shadow-lg shadow-slate-500 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
