                        <h2 class="text-xl font-dosis -mb-2 font-medium text-green-steel">
                            Flexible Shipping Options
                        </h2>
                        <p class="font-open-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
                            We understand that every shipment is unique. We offer total flexibility with shipping options
                            tailored to your needs.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 w-full max-w-md md:w-[48%] xl:w-1/4 min-h-[14rem] xl:-mr-4 p-4 hover:border rounded-md hover:shadow-lg shadow-slate-500 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
                        <div class="text-blue-green text-4xl leading-none">
